{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"1":"Purification (Kitab Al-Taharah)"},"section_detail":{"1":{"hadithnumber_first":1,"hadithnumber_last":390,"arabicnumber_first":1,"arabicnumber_last":390}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":21,"arabicnumber":21,"text":"حدثنا عثمان بن ابي شيبة، حدثنا جرير، عن منصور، عن مجاهد، عن ابن عباس، عن النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم بمعناه قال \" كان لا يستتر من بوله \" . وقال ابو معاوية \" يستنزه","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih Bukhari (216)"}],"reference":{"book":1,"hadith":21}}]}